      <h3 class="heading-small">Ordered list, numbered</h3>

      <ol class="list-number">
        <li>If one, it must be mounted centrally, or if adjacent to another lamp, e.g. one dipped beam lamp and one main beam lamp, they must be mounted symmetrically about the centre.</li>
        <li>If two, they must be symmetrically mounted</li>
        <li>If the maximum vehicle width exceeds 1300mm, two dipped and main beam headlamps are required (1700mm for motorcycle derived tricycles)</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="dev-small">Class: <code>list-number</code></p>

      <h3 class="heading-small">Nested, ordered list, lettered and Roman</h3>

      <ol class="list-alpha" type="a">
        <li>A headlamp:
          <ol class="list-roman" type="i">
            <li>with up to &half; light sources not functioning in the case of LED</li>
            <li>missing, inoperative or more than &half; not functioning in the case of LED.</li>
          </ol>
        </li>
        <li>If two, they must be symmetrically mounted</li>
        <li>If the maximum vehicle width exceeds 1300mm, two dipped and main beam headlamps are required (1700mm for motorcycle derived tricycles)</li>
      </ol>
      <p class="dev-small">Class: <code>list-alpha</code></p>
      <p class="dev-small">Class: <code>list-roman</code></p>

      <h2 class="heading-medium">Tables</h2>

